1. Send a direct message to our @Human Validation Bot in our **TensorAlchemy **Discord server as follows: @Human Validation Bot wallet.

3. Now with your wallet set up, simply cast votes in any of our supported channels. In our TensorAlchemy server, the bot posts a new batch to be voted on every few minutes.

Happy voting! 🧪

1) I would love to be able to remove and redo my votes.  Sometimes a new option comes up while I'm in the middle of assessing images in another window, and when I come back if I don't notice (or it changes while I'm clicking), I'd like to be able to remove and redo my votes.

2) I would love to be able to vote more than once for an image to weight it.  For example, recently there was a set of images where only one image actually hit the mark of the prompt.  I'd love to be able to weight that one image by giving it all three of the votes.
